{"body": "Definitely :-1: for this one. We can't change a core feature like this one to threat hashes in a different way.\r\n\r\nBTW you can use the `store` feature to do the same and get rid of the delegation.\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nclass Order < ActiveRecord::Base\r\n    store :response, accessors: [:code, :message]\r\n\r\n    def place\r\n      # ...\r\n      response = json_response\r\n      save\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee http://api.rubyonrails.org/classes/ActiveRecord/Store.html", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/20665061", "created_at": "2013-07-09T10:19:42Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11262#issuecomment-20665061", "updated_at": "2013-07-09T10:19:42Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11262, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d6ebbd3543c151008328"}, "id": 20665061, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11262"}
